1.1: Fri Nov 28, 2003
	* Added animations to clears and block rotations.
	* Connections are visually shown by highlighting the connecting
	blocks.
	* Game options are now accessed from a screen after pressing "New
	Game."
	* Vast speed improvements with the drawing code.
	* Various UI changes.
	* File formats for high scores and preferences have been changed.

